# CNN Accelerator Simulator

## Build

```bash
cmake -S . -B build-bench
cmake --build build-bench -j
```

## Run

Legacy single run:

```bash
./build-bench/bitserial_sim
```

Outputs:

- `experiment_report.txt`
- `experiment_report.csv`

Benchmark help:

```bash
./build-bench/bitserial_bench --help
```

## Benchmark Modes

- `speed`: timing summary
- `detailed`: full metrics
- `compare`: ET-off vs ET-on summary

## Common Commands

Quick compare:

```bash
./build-bench/bitserial_bench --suite quick --mode compare
```

Full compare suite:

```bash
./build-bench/bitserial_bench \
  --suite all \
  --mode compare \
  --et paired \
  --grouping all \
  --warmup 1 \
  --repetitions 1 \
  --text-out build-bench/full_benchmark_compare.txt \
  --csv-out build-bench/full_benchmark_compare.csv
```

Full detailed suite:

```bash
./build-bench/bitserial_bench \
  --suite all \
  --mode detailed \
  --et paired \
  --grouping all \
  --warmup 1 \
  --repetitions 1 \
  --text-out build-bench/full_benchmark_detailed.txt \
  --csv-out build-bench/full_benchmark_detailed.csv
```

Focused sample 0 compare:

```bash
./build-bench/bitserial_bench \
  --suite quick \
  --mode compare \
  --scenario quick-mnist-sample-0 \
  --text-out build-bench/sample0_compare.txt \
  --csv-out build-bench/sample0_compare.csv
```

Repeated speed run:

```bash
./build-bench/bitserial_bench \
  --suite quick \
  --mode speed \
  --warmup 1 \
  --repetitions 5 \
  --text-out build-bench/quick_speed.txt
```

Extended memory-pressure run:

```bash
./build-bench/bitserial_bench \
  --suite extended \
  --mode detailed \
  --synthetic-profile memory-pressure \
  --grouping ETAwareCostBalancedMemoryAware \
  --et on \
  --csv-out build-bench/memory_pressure_detailed.csv
```

## Useful Flags

```bash
./build-bench/bitserial_bench --grouping OutputChannelModulo
./build-bench/bitserial_bench --grouping ETAwareCostBalancedMemoryAware
./build-bench/bitserial_bench --et paired
./build-bench/bitserial_bench --et off
./build-bench/bitserial_bench --et on
./build-bench/bitserial_bench --scenario quick-mnist-sample-0
./build-bench/bitserial_bench --suite extended --synthetic-profile large
./build-bench/bitserial_bench --suite extended --synthetic-profile memory-pressure
```

Defaults:

- `--suite quick`
- `--mode compare`
- `--grouping all`
- `--et paired`
- `--warmup 1`
- `--repetitions 1`

## Tests

Run all tests:

```bash
cd build-bench
ctest --output-on-failure
```

Individual tests:

```bash
./build-bench/benchmark_helper_tests
./build-bench/benchmark_regression_tests
./build-bench/benchmark_realworld_tests
```

Test coverage:

- `benchmark_helper_tests`: helper math and report formatting
- `benchmark_regression_tests`: sample-0 benchmark invariants
- `benchmark_realworld_tests`: sparse/dense MNIST, speed mode, memory-pressure runs

## Training

```bash
python3 training/train_mnist_cnn.py
```
